   <sect2 role="installation">
      <title>Installation de Shared-desktop-ontologies</title> 
      
      <para>
         Installez <application>shared-desktop-ontologies</application> en lançant les commandes
         suivantes: 
      </para> 
      
<screen><userinput>mkdir build &amp;&amp;
cd build &amp;&amp;
cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=&kde-dir; ..</userinput></screen>
      
      <para>
         Maintenant, en tant qu'utilisateur <systemitem class="username"> root </systemitem>&nbsp;: 
         
      </para> 
      
<screen role="root">
<userinput>make install</userinput></screen>
      
   </sect2>
   
